  <h2 id="tables-responsive-rows-and-cols">Responsive - Mixed rows and columns</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To make columns of <code>&lt;td&gt;</code>s use <code>.t-inline</code>.</li>
    <li>To make rows of <code>&lt;td&gt;</code>s use <code>.t-block</code>.</li>
    <li>To break into a row after a seris of columns, use <code>.t-row-1</code>
