  <h2 id="tables-responsive-column-titles">Responsive - Column Titles</h2>
  <p>Column titles in <code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> are moved to the left as 'row
    titles' on smaller screens.</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Use class <code>table-responsive-column-titles</code> on containing div.</li>
    <li>Any <code>&lt;td&gt;</code> that should become a 'row' title on small
      screens will need a <code>data-title</code> attribute that reflects the
      column title.</li>
    <li>For content that should break out of the table and float right, use
      class <code>mobile-row</code> on <code>&lt;td&gt;</code></li>
    <li>Optionally include a 'mobile sorting' dropdown menu in a <code>&lt;th&gt;</code> in <code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> with class <code>.t-sort</code>. This item will not be visible on large screens and should contain items that reflect the normal column titles. Note this is not required for proper functioning. If omitted, there will simply be no sorting menu.</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="bs-example">
    <div class="table-responsive-column-titles border-top">
      <table class="table table-valign-middle border-top border-bottom">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th class="t-firstname">First Name <span class="lt-icon lt-carat-down lt-medium"></span></th>
            <th class="t-lastname">Last Name <span class="lt-icon lt-carat-down lt-medium"></span></th>
            <th class="t-phone">Phone <span class="lt-icon lt-carat-down lt-medium"></span></th>
            <th><span class="sr-only">Actions</span></th>
            <th class="t-sort text-normal text-muted underline medium pt-0 pb-4">
